B & =(\hat{s}_{1}-\hat{s}_{0})\sqrt{\frac{1}{\frac{\hat{Q}\hat{q}_{0}-\hat{s}_{0}^{2}}{\hat{q}_{0}}+(\hat{s}_{1}-\hat{s}_{0})^{2}}}
